description: President Donald Trump was heading to Florida on Friday, watching Fox News, when he saw the network run a story on how Christians were being targeted by Islamic groups in Nigeria, two sources familiar with the matter told CNN. The president was “immediately” angered by it, one of the sources said, and asked to get further read in on the issue. Shortly after Air Force One touched down in West Palm Beach, he began posting on Truth Social. CNN’s Alayna Treene reports. #CNN #News
fulltitle: Trump ‘immediately’ angered by Fox News segment, threatens action in Nigeria
